<br>
The only way to get Hsagra's Wrath is to get your CoV faction up to Kindly, which means killing lots of giants. Your best bet for that is proably hunting in Kael near the arena for a few nights. Once you have the spell, you can go kill dragons or coldain to get your giant faction back.<br>
<br>
It'll take a ton of kills to swing your faction out and then back, but I don't believe there's any other way. <p>Zwobu &lt;Trade Foundation&gt; Innoruuk<br><img src="http://patriot.net/~josh/zwobu.jpeg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unoonanie.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Noonanie</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/3/01 9:09:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=241.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction questions.</span><hr size=1> <br>
